data.description: Did not flood.  Well laid-out floor plan, large dining open to larger living room.  Central living separates master from other bedrooms.  House well kept, lots of options for updating.  Fresh paint next week (June 2018).  Easy to see, easy to make your own, easy to live in.  Blackwater off main drives, quiet.  New Elementary, quick access to BW8 & I10, lots of restaurants close by.
